Tornados, prevalent in April through June, in a section of America
called "Tornado Alley" often leave a trail of death and millions of
dollars of destruction behind.  Although we are learning more of the
causes, nature and protections against tornadoes, as one of natures
more terrifying phenomena, they cannot be prevented.</SUM>
